Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得在墓地的时候 Jin的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我就想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我没有忘记Jin 就能一直和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着对Jin的记忆 努力地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种特训也是有意义的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而让我意识到这一点的 是御子乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我这样 也说是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次换我来支持御子乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说御子乃也是非常重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 虽然不是你的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要做那样的事呢 不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都开始不了解自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有完全了解自己的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真的全是些不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说御子乃是希尔菲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 而阿波隆就是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 说起不可思议的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外不会亲近他人的修修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却对那个人特别的亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就因为这样 觉得他不是什么坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着阿马塔的时候还要惨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被咬着脸不放什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 现在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初相遇的时候 我就被修修讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这就是说 我配不上御子乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话 这就是命运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我和Mix由洞结缘是天意一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被修修讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在恋爱中败给那个狼崽子也是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切真的已经在一万两千年前就注定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别烦恼了 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 射人先射马
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从和修修搞好关系入手如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共是3450九龙元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先买了貌似能哄修修开心的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算做了这种事也什么都解决不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 能听我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向对方说了不能说的事 要怎么补救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不做也无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起用奇怪的话来搪塞 应该把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了对方好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接了当说出来吧 “我最讨厌你了”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对待男人就必须要时刻保持坚决的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀不好了 安迪还在等我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这完全不能算是答案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是三三区吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速应对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 优先确保市民安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的母亲 奥丽莎锁创造出的Iron C
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誓为这颗星球带来繁荣与平安的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因不明的输出率低下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制系统的故障
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸事故的频发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上不存在什么能永远运作下去的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这未免也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 这就是Altair界走向灭亡的开端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 这是对我的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战演习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 这是不动的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Aquarion互相战斗太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生与死就如同硬币的正反面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是闯过了墓穴特训的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能将所有的危机化作自身的食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着下一个阶段成长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必今后的战斗会越发激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了克服更加艰苦的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个特训是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战Element的分组呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎·铃白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会让Aquarion之间进行模拟战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山茶花·毕安卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和怪炎大人合体?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个莫非是修雷特大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸井·德雷扎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对阵 阿马塔 杰西卡 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各Vector机已经到达对战区域上空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎队用Aquarion GEPART
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔队用Aquarion EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练合体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion GEPART
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方都没有ELement能力的试用限制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们面前的就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好这种打算 竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔 你是否有保护御子乃的力量
